---
import { SITE } from "../data/site";
import BrandMark from "./BrandMark.astro";
---

<footer class="border-t border-border-soft bg-surface">
  <div
    class="mx-auto flex max-w-[1180px] flex-wrap items-start justify-between gap-7 px-8 py-[42px]"
  >
    <div>
      <div class="mb-3 flex items-center gap-2.5">
        <BrandMark box={26} size={14} radius={7} />
        <span class="font-serif text-[17px] font-medium text-ink">{SITE.shortTitle}</span>
      </div>
      <p class="max-w-[44ch] text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted">
        薩爾達傳說 BotW / TotK 技巧與 Glitch 攻略，整理自 {SITE.author} 的 YouTube 頻道。
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3.5 text-[13px] text-muted">
        © 2026 {SITE.author} · 內容整理自個人 YouTube 頻道
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex gap-2.5">
      <a
        href={SITE.youtube}
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
        class="inline-flex items-center rounded-[9px] bg-surface-2 px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-ink no-underline shadow-[0_0_0_1px_var(--border-strong)]"
      >
        YouTube 頻道
      </a>
      <a
        href={SITE.github}
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
        class="inline-flex items-center rounded-[9px] bg-surface-2 px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-ink no-underline shadow-[0_0_0_1px_var(--border-strong)]"
      >
        GitHub
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
